{
  "texts": [
    "Specializing in the accommodation services sector, Hernandez-Bocanegra and Ziegler (2023) provide insights into hotel recommendations derived from reviews.",
    "This system equips users with explanations behind specific hotel recommendations via aggregation of reviews and answers direct factual queries about a specific aspect of a hotel.",
    "It is worth noting that although similar questions are addressed in the systems, a range of different methods are employed to answer them.",
    "Therefore, in the next sub-section we explore which model-agnostic methods are used to answer specific questions.",
    "We omit this analysis for model-specific methods, since these are tailored to their unique contexts and are difficult to compare."
  ]
}